17
00:02:33,153 --> 00:02:34,571
{\an8}Kerja macam mana?

18
00:02:36,114 --> 00:02:37,115
{\an8}Susah,

19
00:02:37,198 --> 00:02:38,491
{\an8}tapi seronok.

20
00:02:42,245 --> 00:02:43,246
{\an8}Aduh, penatnya.

21
00:02:49,460 --> 00:02:51,880
{\an8}Begini pemandangan dari sini rupanya.

22
00:02:51,963 --> 00:02:54,507
{\an8}Boleh nampak gunung-ganang.

23
00:02:54,591 --> 00:02:56,342
Matahari terbenam juga.

24
00:02:58,344 --> 00:03:02,849
Saya kerja hujung minggu dulu.
Nanti saya putuskan cuti belajar atau tak.

25
00:03:03,892 --> 00:03:05,560
Cuti apabila jadi pelatih.

26
00:03:06,227 --> 00:03:07,604
Mohon latihan musim panas.

27
00:03:10,815 --> 00:03:14,527
Lepas jadi pelatih,
awak boleh pindah ke tempat kediaman.

28
00:03:16,362 --> 00:03:17,363
Apa itu?

29
00:03:17,447 --> 00:03:18,281
Asrama.

30
00:03:19,699 --> 00:03:20,700
Asrama?

31
00:03:22,785 --> 00:03:25,121
Boleh masuk asrama lepas jadi pelatih.

32
00:03:25,204 --> 00:03:27,290
Latihan berapa lama?

33
00:03:27,373 --> 00:03:28,875
Bergantung.

34
00:03:28,958 --> 00:03:30,543
Boleh jadi sepanjang musim panas,

35
00:03:30,627 --> 00:03:32,253
