36
00:03:33,212 --> 00:03:35,006
Kalau mereka sediakan asrama,

37
00:03:36,174 --> 00:03:38,885
mesti latihan itu panjang dan susah.

38
00:03:39,552 --> 00:03:41,054
Saya mungkin cuti belajar.

39
00:03:41,930 --> 00:03:43,389
Awak dah pilih fakulti?

40
00:03:44,432 --> 00:03:45,350
