49
00:04:10,792 --> 00:04:12,460
awak pandai lukis sayur.

50
00:04:12,543 --> 00:04:14,045
Memang ada kerja untuk awak.

51
00:04:14,754 --> 00:04:17,799
Tak sangka awak ingat.

52
00:04:24,764 --> 00:04:28,017
{\an8}Pandai lukis sayur mungkin tak berguna.

53
00:04:29,602 --> 00:04:31,688
Harap kerja yang guna bahasa Inggeris.

54
00:04:31,771 --> 00:04:33,564
Saya pandai berbual kosong.

55
00:04:33,648 --> 00:04:36,067
Sebelum So-hyeon datang,
saya selalu berbual

56
00:04:36,150 --> 00:04:38,111
dengan tetamu waktu tak ramai.

57
00:04:38,194 --> 00:04:40,446
Saya boleh bercakap Inggeris dengan yakin.
Hebat, bukan?

58
00:04:41,698 --> 00:04:42,573
Terujanya dia.

59
00:04:43,950 --> 00:04:44,784
Ya.

60
00:04:46,077 --> 00:04:48,329
Dulu impian nak berdikari saya samar,

61
00:04:48,413 --> 00:04:50,164
sekarang dah makin jelas.

62
00:04:51,165 --> 00:04:52,750
Ini yang orang panggil peluang.

63
00:05:02,844 --> 00:05:06,097
Sekarang kerja hujung minggu,
lama-lama hari minggu.

64
00:05:07,098 --> 00:05:08,599
Saya cuma lapang hujung minggu.

65
00:05:09,392 --> 00:05:12,437
- Nak selaraskan jadual kita…
- Kalau malam Jumaat?

66
00:05:13,980 --> 00:05:16,357
- Kita cuba.
- Ya.

67
00:05:18,359 --> 00:05:21,154
Kalau memang takdir, ia tak samar.

68
00:05:21,237 --> 00:05:23,406
Ia jelas. Kita tak teragak-agak.

69
00:05:24,490 --> 00:05:28,161
Mungkin itulah cara orang cari arah hidup
dan terus maju.

70
00:05:29,245 --> 00:05:32,165
Saya tertanya-tanya. Jelas macam mana?

71
00:05:33,082 --> 00:05:34,459
Saya boleh rasa.

72
00:05:34,542 --> 00:05:37,587
Sebab awak, saya tahu
macam mana rasanya takdir.

73
00:05:39,922 --> 00:05:41,549
Jadi, kenapa saya tak tahu?

74
00:05:43,176 --> 00:05:45,094
Lepas awak tahu nanti, hah!

75
00:05:45,178 --> 00:05:48,306
Rasanya kuat dan jelas. Cuba fikir semula.

76
00:05:50,391 --> 00:05:51,476
Hah?

77
00:05:52,643 --> 00:05:53,936
Saya dah rasa banyak kali.

78
00:05:54,687 --> 00:05:55,897
Bila awak rasa?

79
00:05:59,901 --> 00:06:01,736
Apa? Bila?

80
00:06:03,446 --> 00:06:07,241
Masa awak terhuyung-hayang
seolah-olah hampir pengsan

81
00:06:07,325 --> 00:06:09,035
masa melintas padang sekolah.

82
00:06:09,702 --> 00:06:12,497
Saya? Tak ada.
Saya tak pernah terhuyung-hayang.

83
00:06:13,206 --> 00:06:15,166
Maaf. Saya tolak kuat sangat?

84
00:06:16,084 --> 00:06:17,126
Hei!

85
00:06:17,919 --> 00:06:20,838
Nampaknya awak dah okey
saya balik seorang diri?

86
00:06:21,839 --> 00:06:22,840
Awak sedih?

87
00:06:24,592 --> 00:06:25,593
Sikit.

88
00:06:26,928 --> 00:06:28,054
Awak dah boleh terima.

89
00:06:28,137 --> 00:06:29,472
Selamat tinggal.

90
00:06:48,241 --> 00:06:49,450
Malam Sabtu saya datang.

91
00:06:51,869 --> 00:06:55,498
Kalau saya bertolak lepas tutoran,
saya sampai pukul 11.00…

92
00:06:57,416 --> 00:06:59,418
Saya tak pernah boleh terima

93
00:06:59,502 --> 00:07:01,212
awak pergi seorang diri.

94
00:07:02,213 --> 00:07:03,214
Okey?

95
00:07:13,724 --> 00:07:16,060
"Saya harap encik seronok ada di sini."

96
00:07:19,021 --> 00:07:22,358
"Saya harap encik seronok ada di sini."
Ada di sini?

97
00:07:24,569 --> 00:07:25,570
"Ada di sini."

98
00:07:26,279 --> 00:07:27,780
Kita akan ke ruang kerja.

99
00:07:27,864 --> 00:07:29,073
- Baiklah.
- Baiklah.

100
00:07:42,253 --> 00:07:43,504
Tetamu masih ada.

101
00:07:44,255 --> 00:07:45,715
Okey. Syabas hari ini.

102
00:07:48,759 --> 00:07:50,845
{\an8}HOTEL SAINT OCEAN
PROGRAM LATIHAN MUSIM PANAS

103
00:07:50,928 --> 00:07:53,347
{\an8}KELEBIHAN LATIHAN
ASRAMA PERCUMA DISEDIAKAN

104
00:08:04,734 --> 00:08:06,152
Penatnya.

105
00:08:10,072 --> 00:08:12,241
Tapi seronok.

106
00:08:16,787 --> 00:08:17,622
<i>Tae-seo.</i>

107
00:08:50,071 --> 00:08:51,072
Makanan okey?

108
00:08:51,155 --> 00:08:53,908
- Semuanya diatur elok dan sedap.
- Terima kasih.

109
00:08:53,991 --> 00:08:55,076
Perlukan apa-apa lagi?

110
00:08:55,159 --> 00:08:56,410
Makanan sangat banyak.

111
00:08:56,494 --> 00:08:58,704
- Nanti kami beritahu.
- Terima kasih.

112
00:08:58,788 --> 00:08:59,914
Kita cuba ikut susunan.

113
00:09:15,513 --> 00:09:16,806
Saya masuk.

114
00:09:46,752 --> 00:09:49,213
Nampaknya Eun-a kepenatan.

115
00:09:49,964 --> 00:09:51,424
Mesti kerja dia sukar.

116
00:09:52,174 --> 00:09:53,175
Saya tak tahu.

117
00:09:53,801 --> 00:09:54,760
Tanya dia sendiri.

118
00:09:56,220 --> 00:09:57,597
Dia takkan beritahu saya.

119
00:09:58,764 --> 00:10:00,975
Ini dimasak dengan sangat sedap.

120
00:10:01,058 --> 00:10:02,810
Boleh hantar pada dia sebelum habis?

121
00:10:02,893 --> 00:10:04,770
Bukankah dia tak nak
sebab menggemukkan?

122
00:10:06,397 --> 00:10:08,858
Mereka panggil saya. Hantarlah sendiri.

123
00:10:09,567 --> 00:10:10,651
Dia takkan makan.

124
00:10:10,735 --> 00:10:11,902
Jangan takut pada dia.

125
00:10:13,029 --> 00:10:15,781
Pergi jumpa dan tanya dia semuanya.

126
00:10:23,331 --> 00:10:24,373
Tunggu sekejap.

127
00:10:24,457 --> 00:10:26,250
- Apa dia?
- Itukah?

128
00:10:30,212 --> 00:10:31,047
Eun-a.

129
00:10:32,006 --> 00:10:33,090
Eun-a!

130
00:10:42,058 --> 00:10:44,852
Kenapa kamu berdua
rahsiakan hubungan kamu?

131
00:10:45,978 --> 00:10:48,939
Kami mula bercinta tahun akhir sekolah,

132
00:10:49,023 --> 00:10:51,025
kami tak nak keluarga kami risau.

133
00:10:51,651 --> 00:10:55,321
Sekarang dah tak perlu rahsiakan,
tapi kami dah terbiasa.

134
00:10:56,113 --> 00:10:57,573
Kami takkan buat lagi.

135
00:10:57,657 --> 00:10:58,991
Tahulah kami.

136
00:10:59,075 --> 00:11:00,951
Tak boleh turun bercakap dengan kami?

137
00:11:04,872 --> 00:11:06,332
Saya faham.

138
00:11:06,999 --> 00:11:09,168
Ini pekan kecil, nanti orang mengata.

139
00:11:09,794 --> 00:11:10,795
Betul.

140
00:11:12,463 --> 00:11:14,882
Okey, kita rahsiakan.
Saya pun akan kunci mulut.

141
00:11:16,926 --> 00:11:18,594
Awak guna pencegahan hamil?

142
00:11:20,721 --> 00:11:22,556
Kami belum…

143
00:11:24,392 --> 00:11:25,976
Lepas ini hati-hati.

144
00:11:26,060 --> 00:11:29,230
Jangan berlagak macam mak saya, So-hyeon.

145
00:11:29,313 --> 00:11:30,481
Saya ada salah cakap?

146
00:11:31,148 --> 00:11:32,733
Awak dah 20 tahun.

147
00:11:32,817 --> 00:11:34,068
Bukan muda lagi.

148
00:11:34,652 --> 00:11:36,320
Kena hati-hati bab-bab ini.

149
00:12:03,764 --> 00:12:04,765
Memalukan.

150
00:12:17,570 --> 00:12:18,696
Awak pun satu.

151
00:12:18,779 --> 00:12:22,658
Awak tak menyibuk
atau ajar apa nak buat pun.

152
00:12:23,993 --> 00:12:26,328
Takkan saya nak mengajar awak pula?

153
00:12:27,163 --> 00:12:29,665
Saya cuma boleh tunggu
perasaan awak reda.

154
00:12:38,883 --> 00:12:40,342
Dia akan kahwini ayah saya.

155
00:12:41,469 --> 00:12:43,012
Saya suka ayah saya nak kahwin,

156
00:12:44,305 --> 00:12:46,474
tapi saya tak kenal dia macam mana.

157
00:12:47,766 --> 00:12:50,978
Dia kata dia lahir di Hawaii,
tapi dia fasih bahasa Korea.

158
00:12:51,061 --> 00:12:52,521
Saya fikir dia penipu.

159
00:12:54,190 --> 00:12:56,525
Tapi dia pergi petik sayur dengan ayah

160
00:12:56,609 --> 00:12:58,027
dan buat semua kerja berat.

161
00:12:59,111 --> 00:13:01,989
Sekejap saya rasa baguslah
ayah ada orang macam dia,

162
00:13:02,740 --> 00:13:03,991
sekejap saya rasa tak.

163
00:13:06,202 --> 00:13:07,203
Apa pun,

164
00:13:07,286 --> 00:13:08,621
saya resah di rumah.

165
00:13:09,538 --> 00:13:11,123
Saya patut cepat-cepat keluar.

166
00:13:14,126 --> 00:13:15,836
Itu menjawab semua soalan

167
00:13:16,921 --> 00:13:18,088
dalam kepala awak?

168
00:13:22,593 --> 00:13:23,594
Bukan apa…

169
00:13:24,512 --> 00:13:27,056
Saya cuma nak beritahu awak
cerita indah-indah saja.

170
00:13:27,932 --> 00:13:29,391
Saya tak nak cerita masalah.

171
00:13:30,351 --> 00:13:32,603
Saya nampak macam masih meratapi?

172
00:13:34,647 --> 00:13:35,856
Taklah.

173
00:13:37,566 --> 00:13:38,609
Tapi entahlah.

174
00:13:40,194 --> 00:13:42,613
Akhirnya saya beritahu juga semua benda.

175
00:13:44,240 --> 00:13:45,241
Eun-a,

176
00:13:48,160 --> 00:13:49,203
saya tak apa-apa.

177
00:13:51,747 --> 00:13:55,251
Awak boleh terus beritahu saya
kalau awak susah.

178
00:13:57,169 --> 00:14:00,130
Beritahu ketika awak buntu,
bukan selepas itu.

179
00:14:00,839 --> 00:14:02,883
Walaupun saya mungkin tak ada jawapan.

180
00:14:06,720 --> 00:14:07,721
Okey.

181
00:14:16,021 --> 00:14:17,439
Eun-a, pandang saya.

182
00:14:18,691 --> 00:14:21,652
Awak kata awak tenang kalau pandang saya.

183
00:14:21,735 --> 00:14:22,778
Pandang.

184
00:15:07,489 --> 00:15:14,455
{\an8}JUN

185
00:15:16,415 --> 00:15:19,501
Saya dah mula tulis tesis,
tapi baru draf saja.

186
00:15:19,585 --> 00:15:22,504
Tajuknya pengawal AI, sangat menarik.

187
00:15:23,130 --> 00:15:26,258
Awak guna kaedah pembelajaran AI apa?

188
00:15:26,342 --> 00:15:27,927
Kaedah pembelajaran pengukuhan.

189
00:15:29,053 --> 00:15:31,263
Saya baca kajian tentang itu.
Nak saya cari?

190
00:15:31,931 --> 00:15:32,973
Boleh juga.

191
00:15:34,934 --> 00:15:36,602
Nak ke makmal cuti nanti?

192
00:15:37,186 --> 00:15:38,938
Seronok belajar di sana musim cuti.

193
00:15:40,272 --> 00:15:42,608
Mungkin awak boleh jadi ahli makmal.

194
00:15:43,317 --> 00:15:44,610
Awak akan sambung siswazah.

195
00:15:45,778 --> 00:15:48,072
- Saya belum fikir.
- Yakah?

196
00:15:48,155 --> 00:15:51,116
Awak jenis suka belajar.
Orang macam awak biasanya di makmal.

197
00:15:51,951 --> 00:15:53,285
Saya jenis macam mana?

198
00:15:53,369 --> 00:15:54,662
Awak?

199
00:15:54,745 --> 00:15:56,622
Awak faham persamaan secara fizikal.

200
00:15:56,705 --> 00:15:59,792
Orang yang cuba memahami makna
akan tertumpu pada inti sesuatu.

201
00:16:00,376 --> 00:16:01,502
Buat apa awak suka.

202
00:16:04,421 --> 00:16:08,217
Bolehkah menyukai sesuatu
jadi sebab untuk apa yang kita buat?

203
00:16:08,968 --> 00:16:10,970
Mestilah. Kalau tak, sebab apa?

204
00:16:13,222 --> 00:16:16,850
Keadaan, situasi atau tanggungjawab?

205
00:16:19,061 --> 00:16:20,229
Kali pertama dengar.

206
00:16:20,813 --> 00:16:22,731
Orang dah tak tentukan berdasarkan itu.

207
00:16:22,815 --> 00:16:24,108
Mereka fokus pada diri.

208
00:16:25,317 --> 00:16:27,945
Apa pun, datanglah cuti musim panas nanti.

209
00:16:30,406 --> 00:16:32,574
Bukan mudah kami ajak orang luar.

210
00:16:32,658 --> 00:16:34,201
Saya tahu.

211
00:16:36,578 --> 00:16:38,247
Boleh saya sambung baca?

212
00:16:38,330 --> 00:16:39,665
Boleh. Awak orang kuat kami.

213
00:16:40,624 --> 00:16:42,960
- Saya nak pergi jumpa profesor.
- Terima kasih.

214
00:16:43,043 --> 00:16:43,877
Baik.

215
00:17:11,238 --> 00:17:13,115
<i>Awak buat apa? Dalam kelas?</i>

216
00:17:13,782 --> 00:17:15,743
<i>Saya ada masa senggang, saya di makmal.</i>

217
00:17:16,368 --> 00:17:17,703
<i>Bila kita nak jumpa?</i>

218
00:17:18,495 --> 00:17:20,581
<i>Tengok jadual. Bila awak lapang?</i>

219
00:17:24,418 --> 00:17:25,961
<i>Kalau malam Rabu?</i>

220
00:17:26,712 --> 00:17:29,548
<i>Ada tutoran, tak boleh tukar masa.</i>
<i>Peperiksaan dah dekat.</i>

221
00:17:30,466 --> 00:17:33,510
<i>Jumaat habis pukul 7.00 malam.</i>
<i>Masuk semula tengah hari Sabtu.</i>

222
00:17:34,845 --> 00:17:36,221
<i>Kalau Sabtu pagi?</i>

223
00:17:36,305 --> 00:17:40,142
SABTU
BUAT PERSEDIAAN PEPERIKSAAN

224
00:17:41,602 --> 00:17:43,937
<i>Boleh. Nanti saya datang.</i>

225
00:17:51,403 --> 00:17:53,155
SEONG-CHAN

226
00:18:08,337 --> 00:18:09,171
Ya?

227
00:18:09,254 --> 00:18:10,506
<i>Awak masih di hotel?</i>

228
00:18:11,090 --> 00:18:13,092
Pasukan GRO mencari pelatih.

229
00:18:14,009 --> 00:18:15,302
GRO itu apa?

230
00:18:16,053 --> 00:18:17,638
<i>Kerja di ruang VIP.</i>

231
00:18:17,721 --> 00:18:19,681
<i>Awak mungkin ada kelebihan.</i>

232
00:18:19,765 --> 00:18:22,392
Tetamu di sini selalu ke tempat awak.

233
00:18:23,018 --> 00:18:24,895
<i>Jabatan ini sesuai dengan awak.</i>

234
00:18:25,479 --> 00:18:26,605
Kena sangatlah.

235
00:18:27,481 --> 00:18:29,024
